             sworn. - I am an apprentice to Mr. 
               <persName id="t18000917-15-person190">
                  Jonathan 
                  Sparrow
               <interp inst="t18000917-15-person190" type="surname" value="Sparrow"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000917-15-person190" type="given" value="Jonathan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000917-15-person190" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
